  "guide_game_title": "🌌 Space Empire: Idle Tycoon",
  "guide_lore_p1": "In 2157 AD, humanity built settlements across the solar system, mining resources and pushing into space. As CEO of 'Space Empire Inc.', you must build your first base in the asteroid belt and construct a space empire.",
  "guide_lore_p2": "Starting from a small mine, work your way up to drone hubs, refineries, power plants, and outposts — each building generates rent and resources. Reinvest profits to upgrade buildings, raise your Fame, and unlock advanced tech and structures.",
  "guide_lore_p3": "Build a fleet to crush pirates, explore planets to establish colonies, and advance your technology through research. Your ultimate goal: become a space billionaire.",
  "guide_goals_title": "🎯 Game Goals",
  "guide_goal_primary": "Primary Goal:",
  "guide_goal_primary_desc": "Reach 1,000,000,000 (1B) total wealth → Ending",
  "guide_goal_advanced": "Advanced Goals:",
  "guide_goal_advanced_desc": "Prestige for permanent bonuses, complete achievements, clear challenge modes, interact with alien races",
  "guide_goal_final": "Final Goal:",
  "guide_goal_final_desc": "Awaken all buildings, complete all research, max out your fleet, reach high transcendence levels",
  "guide_newbie_title": "📋 Getting Started Guide",
  "guide_step1_title": "1️⃣ Build Your Base (💰 Earn Money)",
  "guide_step1_body": "💸 Click to earn gold. Once you save up, build a Surface Mine. Buildings generate passive income every second. Use that income to build more and upgrade.",
  "guide_step2_title": "2️⃣ Raise Awareness (📡 Fame)",
  "guide_step2_body": "Building and upgrading structures increases your Fame. Reaching certain Fame thresholds unlocks new buildings and ships.",
  "guide_step3_title": "3️⃣ Build a Fleet (🚀 Ships)",
  "guide_step3_body": "Start with 2 Scouts and 1 Corvette. Build more ships to hunt pirates and collect loot.",
  "guide_step4_title": "4️⃣ Research (🔬 Technology)",
  "guide_step4_body": "Research provides permanent bonuses to building efficiency, Fame gain, combat power, and more. Choose wisely as research takes time.",
  "guide_step5_title": "5️⃣ Explore & Colonize (🌍 Colonization)",
  "guide_step5_body": "Build colony ships to explore planets. Successful colonization lets you establish colonies, each offering unique traits and bonuses.",
  "guide_step6_title": "6️⃣ Prestige & Transcend (✨ Rebirth)",
  "guide_step6_body": "Once strong enough, prestige to earn permanent income multipliers. Transcendence consumes Awakening Stones for per-level permanent buffs.",
  "guide_building_system_title": "🏗️ Building System",
  "guide_building_system_1": "• 10 building types, each producing specific resources and generating rent.",
  "guide_building_system_2": "• Building prices fluctuate in real-time from Fire Sale (×0.5) to Ultra Premium (×2.0).",
  "guide_building_system_3": "• Each upgrade increases income and resource production by 12%.",
  "guide_building_system_4": "• Reach max level (LV20) and Awaken to activate unique building effects.",
  "guide_combat_system_title": "🚀 Ships & Combat System",
  "guide_combat_system_1": "• Build 11 ship types to form your fleet.",
  "guide_combat_system_2": "• Each ship has type advantage against certain pirates.",
  "guide_combat_system_3": "• Pirates grow stronger with each wave.",
  "guide_combat_system_4": "• Scouts have special abilities that discover items.",
  "guide_tips_title": "💡 Beginner Tips",
  "guide_tip_1": "• 🎯 Build and upgrade mines first.",
  "guide_tip_2": "• 🎯 Buy buildings during ⬇️⬇️ Fire Sale (×0.5) pricing.",
  "guide_tip_3": "• 🎯 Prioritize 'Building Management' and 'Awareness Spread' research.",
  "guide_tip_4": "• 🎯 Build ships that counter pirate types for efficiency.",
